headline: Trane Technologies to Acquire BrainBox AI
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, December 18, 2024--Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT), a global climate innovator, announced that it has signed a definitive agreement to acquire BrainBox AI, a pioneer in autonomous HVAC controls and generative Artificial Intelligence (AI) building technology.

headline: This High-Performing ETF Paves the Way to a Nearly $1 Trillion Investment Opportunity
summary: America's infrastructure is in pretty rough shape.  The American Society of Civil Engineers barely gave a passing grade to the country's infrastructure (C-) when it provided its last report card in 2021.  The Global X U.S. Infrastructure Development ETF invests in companies that should benefit from increased spending on U.S. infrastructure.
